<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> – Kishore Orthopedic Clinic</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <!-- Page Hero with image background -->
    <section class="page-hero page-hero--image" style="background-image: url('/images/surgery.png');">
      <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="container page-hero__content" style="text-align:center;">
        <span class="section-tag section-tag--light">Our Story</span>
        <h1>Vijayawada's Trusted Choice<br>for Orthopedic Excellence</h1>
        <p>Specialised orthopedic care — built on international training, advanced techniques and a genuine commitment to every patient's recovery.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission / About -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-story">
          <div class="about-story__text">
            <span class="section-tag">Our Mission</span>
            <h2>Restoring Lives, One Patient at a Time</h2>
            <p>At Kishore Orthopedic Clinic, we believe that every patient deserves expert, compassionate care that treats the whole person — not just the injury. Our practice is built on trust, transparency and a deep respect for the lives we are privileged to help restore.</p>
            <p>Led by Dr. M. Kishore Kumar, our clinic specialises in complex orthopedic conditions — from spinal disorders and joint replacements to limb reconstruction and sports injuries. Every treatment plan is guided by the latest evidence-based techniques and the surgeon's extensive international fellowship training.</p>
            <p>From your first consultation through surgery and into rehabilitation, we are with you at every step — focused on one goal: getting you back to the life you love.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-story__visual">
            <div class="about-visual-card">
              <div class="about-visual-card__logo">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Kishore Orthopedic Clinic" style="width:72px;height:72px;object-fit:contain;" />
              </div>
              <h3>Kishore Orthopedic Clinic</h3>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Sri Devi Apartments, Old Checkpost<br>Vijayawada – 520007</p>
              <div class="about-badges">
                <span class="about-badge">MS / DNB Ortho</span>
                <span class="about-badge">MCH Ortho</span>
                <span class="about-badge">FISS Spine</span>
                <span class="about-badge">4 Int'l Fellowships</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Our Values</span>
          <h2>What Drives Everything We Do</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-4">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/compassion.jpg" alt="Compassion" class="value-img" />
            </div>
            <h3>Compassion</h3>
            <p>We treat every patient with the warmth and empathy we would want for our own family members.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/excellence.jpg" alt="Excellence" class="value-img value-img--pad" />
            </div>
            <h3>Excellence</h3>
            <p>We continuously raise the bar on surgical outcomes, patient experience and clinical standards.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/integrity.jpg" alt="Integrity" class="value-img value-img--pad" />
            </div>
            <h3>Integrity</h3>
            <p>Honest, transparent communication and ethical practice are the foundation of every patient relationship.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/innovation.jpg" alt="Innovation" class="value-img" />
            </div>
            <h3>Innovation</h3>
            <p>We embrace the latest medical advances to offer our patients safer, faster and more effective treatments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Journey -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Academic & Fellowship Background</span>
          <h2>Dr. M. Kishore Kumar — Qualifications</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="journey-grid">
          <div class="journey-col">
            <h3 class="journey-col__heading">Academic Degrees</h3>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--degree">MBBS</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Bachelor of Medicine & Bachelor of Surgery</strong>
                <span>Rangaraya Medical College, Kakinada</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--degree">MS (Ortho)</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Master of Surgery – Orthopaedics</strong>
                <span>Andhra Medical College, Visakhapatnam</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--degree">DNB (Ortho)</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Diplomate of National Board – Orthopaedics</strong>
                <span>K.S. Hegde Medical Academy, Mangalore</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--degree">MCH (Ortho)</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Master of Chirurgiae – Orthopaedics</strong>
                <span>University of Seychelles American Institute of Medicine (USAIM)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="journey-divider"></div>
          <div class="journey-col">
            <h3 class="journey-col__heading">International Fellowships</h3>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--fellow">Fellowship</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Fellow in Arthroscopy</strong>
                <span>Aware Global Hospital, Hyderabad</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--fellow">Fellowship</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Fellow in Arthroplasty</strong>
                <span>Sunshine Hospital, Secunderabad</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--intl">International</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Fellow in Ilizarov & Limb Reconstruction</strong>
                <span>Russian Ilizarov Scientific Center, Kurgan, Russia</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-item">
              <div class="journey-badge journey-badge--intl">International</div>
              <div class="journey-item__content">
                <strong>Fellow in Spine Surgery — FISS</strong>
                <span>Cantonal Hospital Fribourg, Switzerland</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- International Fellowship Showcase -->
    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="fellowship-section">
          <div class="fellowship-content">
            <span class="section-tag">International Training</span>
            <h2>Fellowship-Trained at World-Class Institutions</h2>
            <p style="color:#64748b;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Dr. M. Kishore Kumar holds four international fellowships — a rare distinction that brings globally proven surgical techniques directly to patients in Vijayawada.</p>
            <ul class="fellowship-list">
              <li>
                <div class="fellowship-icon">✦</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Ilizarov & Limb Reconstruction</strong>
                  <span>Russian Scientific Centre "Named after Ilizarov", Kurgan, Russia</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="fellowship-icon">✦</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Spine Surgery — FISS</strong>
                  <span>Fellowship of International Spine Study Group, Switzerland</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="fellowship-icon">✦</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Arthroscopy & Joint Replacement</strong>
                  <span>Advanced arthroscopic techniques and minimally invasive joint procedures</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="fellowship-icon">✦</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Complex Trauma & Reconstruction</strong>
                  <span>Flap coverage, bone reconstruction and polytrauma management</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="expertise-actions">
              <a href="/doctors" class="btn btn-primary">Meet Dr. Kishore</a>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fellowship-image">
            <img src="/images/kishore-russia.png" alt="Dr. M. Kishore Kumar at the Ilizarov Centre, Kurgan Russia" class="fellowship-img" />
            <div class="fellowship-caption">
              Dr. M. Kishore Kumar receiving his fellowship certificate at the Russian Scientific Centre "Named after Ilizarov", Kurgan, Russia
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
